name: BlockChain Barcodes 03 - Do Your Own Research
description: BlockChain Barcodes are a collection of phrases common in our community that have been translated from an ASCI string into binary and then represented as a Code 128 Standard barcode that can be read with a barcode scanning app. Included in the footer is the original string to juxtapose the digitization of the human experience and consider the abstraction of data into art.
